00:24:03.806 --> 00:24:08.361
A great poet Kabira has said: "If by shaving your hair,

00:24:08.562 --> 00:24:10.562
if you are going to get your Nirvana,

00:24:10.763 --> 00:24:17.601
then the sheep who it is shaved every year will go there first."

