00:24:53.602 --> 00:24:58.924
and I am supposed to wear only dot, whether it is cold or not."

00:24:59.168 --> 00:25:04.894
And he said, "That is how it is I am going to get my Nirvana."

00:25:05.423 --> 00:25:09.259
I said, "In India, 80% people wear dots,

00:25:09.460 --> 00:25:14.475
if they are going to get Nirvana, then where you will be?"

00:25:15.398 --> 00:25:18.156
There is another really shocking thing.

00:25:18.357 --> 00:25:24.732
In Cabella, one fellow came and he told Me, that "I have become a very poor man,

00:25:24.933 --> 00:25:30.147
because all my money I have given to Dalai Lama."

00:25:30.452 --> 00:25:37.913
So in the name of God, how many types of people there are who are cheating,

00:25:38.395 --> 00:25:44.574
I have to tell you all these things because I am your Mother.

00:25:44.871 --> 00:25:48.621
I am not afraid of them.

00:25:48.822 --> 00:25:52.129
I am only afraid that you people are great seekers

00:25:52.330 --> 00:25:56.941
and you should not be lost.

00:25:57.538 --> 00:26:01.479
Guru Nanak has said, "The one who is a real master

00:26:01.680 --> 00:26:06.608
is the one who makes you meet the Divine."

00:26:06.809 --> 00:26:12.111
Christ also said that "You are to be born again."

00:26:12.312 --> 00:26:17.929
In Sanskrit, we have the word called "dwija" for a bird

00:26:18.130 --> 00:26:23.098
and also for an enlighten soul.

00:26:23.350 --> 00:26:30.427
That means a person who is born again like the bird.

00:26:31.143 --> 00:26:36.994
The bird is first an egg and then it becomes a bird,

00:26:37.195 --> 00:26:41.460
it has a second birth.

00:26:41.945 --> 00:26:45.530
In the same way, we have to have our second birth,

00:26:45.731 --> 00:26:49.858
where you get complete transformation.

00:26:51.468 --> 00:26:54.305
As it is, several people have that,

00:26:54.506 --> 00:26:59.271
"we are born again, we are Christians, Hindus, Muslims",

00:26:59.472 --> 00:27:03.534
these are nothing but brands.

00:27:04.001 --> 00:27:07.594
You maybe are a Christian, Hindu, Muslim, anything,

00:27:07.795 --> 00:27:13.912
but you can commit any mistake and can commit any sin.

00:27:14.481 --> 00:27:19.777
In Sahaja Yoga, you become, becoming is the point.

00:27:20.171 --> 00:27:24.999
And when the Kundalini pierces through your fontanel bone area,

00:27:25.200 --> 00:27:29.887
is the actualization of your baptism, actualization.

00:27:30.088 --> 00:27:34.971
It is the experience of feeling the Divine.

00:27:35.708 --> 00:27:41.371
Is not a lecture or it is not a sermon.

00:27:43.108 --> 00:27:46.624
But the greatest thing that happens to you

00:27:46.825 --> 00:27:50.865
that you jump in the ocean of joy.

00:27:52.296 --> 00:27:58.655
Happiness and unhappiness are two sides of a coin.

00:28:00.470 --> 00:28:05.243
But joy is singular.

00:28:05.723 --> 00:28:10.684
Where you become the source of peace

00:28:10.885 --> 00:28:15.108
and you witness the whole world as a drama.

00:28:15.471 --> 00:28:22.127
But you yourself become the light of peace and joy.

00:28:23.111 --> 00:28:27.697
Sahaja Yoga is working in 55 nations now.

00:28:27.898 --> 00:28:32.718
And I am amazed that I've never seen anybody quarreling,

00:28:32.919 --> 00:28:37.145
fighting or even arguing.

00:28:37.868 --> 00:28:42.024
They all enjoy each others company.

00:28:42.286 --> 00:28:46.059
Such pure love, friendship

00:28:46.260 --> 00:28:50.471
that you really feel a new age has started.

00:28:50.672 --> 00:28:57.954
Very pure relationships of husband and wife, sisters, brothers,

00:28:58.155 --> 00:29:00.936
I've never heard somebody running away with somebody's wife

00:29:01.137 --> 00:29:05.543
or somebody's husband in Sahaja Yoga.

00:29:05.744 --> 00:29:13.923
I really know there are so many great
souls who want to be born on this Earth.

00:29:14.331 --> 00:29:22.701
And if they are born to non Sahaja Yogi, they will never understand their children.

00:29:23.632 --> 00:29:29.600
Moreover they are anxious to be born to Sahaja Yogis.

00:29:30.438 --> 00:29:37.446
In this lecture, I cannot tell you everything about Sahaja Yoga, I'm sorry.

00:29:38.151 --> 00:29:44.479
Only in English language, I must have addressed five thousand lectures so far.

00:29:45.325 --> 00:29:50.270
But it is like this, we have so many beautiful lights here.

00:29:50.894 --> 00:29:56.620
And we have to just put on one switch and all the lights come in.

00:29:57.681 --> 00:30:01.892
Because it is built in.

00:30:02.093 --> 00:30:06.234
In the same way, it is built in within you.

00:30:06.833 --> 00:30:11.035
This is your own power.

00:30:11.236 --> 00:30:15.431
This is your own glory.

00:30:16.157 --> 00:30:20.329
All your protection powers will manifest.

00:30:20.899 --> 00:30:27.641
So many artists, musicians have become world famous today.

00:30:28.280 --> 00:30:35.631
You will be happy to know this time, Miss Universe was a Sahaja Yogini.

00:30:36.426 --> 00:30:40.340
She is going to see Me and she said, "I don't want to wear funny dresses."

00:30:40.541 --> 00:30:44.431
I said, "No, you can wear, if you can wear swimming dresses,

00:30:44.632 --> 00:30:48.839
is alright, doesn't matter, you go ahead."

00:30:49.040 --> 00:30:54.000
She is a very simple, intelligent girl.

00:30:54.853 --> 00:30:57.337
I wouldn't say she is a beauty or anything

00:30:57.538 --> 00:31:01.907
according to Hollywood standards.

00:31:02.212 --> 00:31:08.517
But her innocence and her pose or her intelligence

00:31:08.718 --> 00:31:15.320
has achieved this wisdom for her that she is today Miss Universe.

00:31:15.835 --> 00:31:19.819
So is a very remarkable thing that we don't know

00:31:20.020 --> 00:31:26.582
what qualities we have, what potential we have, how dynamic people we are.

00:31:26.963 --> 00:31:31.231
It is like a candle which is not get enlightened

00:31:31.432 --> 00:31:38.034
but a enlightened candle can enlighten the one which is not enlightened.

00:31:39.183 --> 00:31:45.756
This is like is a seed, if it is embedded in the Mother Earth,

00:31:45.957 --> 00:31:50.792
it sprouts spontaneously, sahaja.

00:31:51.380 --> 00:31:54.633
Because the seed as well the Mother Earth

00:31:54.834 --> 00:31:59.177
has the built in quality to sprout.

00:31:59.519 --> 00:32:04.909
So believe Me, all of you have got this.

00:32:05.110 --> 00:32:09.245
And it will work out.

00:32:09.461 --> 00:32:13.843
Please have no doubts about yourself.

00:32:14.044 --> 00:32:19.719
Another thing is that this Power that is in the triangular bone

00:32:19.920 --> 00:32:24.623
is the Power of Pure Desire.

00:32:25.132 --> 00:32:29.420
All desires are not pure.

00:32:29.968 --> 00:32:33.813
You want to have house today, then you want to have a car,

00:32:34.014 --> 00:32:39.707
then want to have a helicopter, I don't know, goes on like that.

00:32:39.968 --> 00:32:43.197
There is no end.

00:32:43.456 --> 00:32:50.354
According to economics: wants are not satiable in general.

00:32:50.904 --> 00:32:59.458
Because they are not pure wants, pure desires.

00:32:59.811 --> 00:33:03.814
So you should have full confidence and also should have

00:33:04.015 --> 00:33:09.724
desire to be one with the Divine Power.

00:33:10.715 --> 00:33:15.778
I cannot force on you, you have to ask for it.

00:33:17.627 --> 00:33:21.751
Because I respect your freedom.

00:33:22.391 --> 00:33:27.101
This Power is your individual Mother.

00:33:27.711 --> 00:33:32.004
She knows everything about you.

00:33:32.205 --> 00:33:37.319
Like a tape recorder, She knows what are your desires,

00:33:37.520 --> 00:33:41.527
what are your aspirations.

00:33:42.470 --> 00:33:47.876
And She is very anxious to give you your second birth.

00:33:48.446 --> 00:33:53.668
And as when you were born, your mother took all the troubles,

00:33:53.869 --> 00:33:58.547
this Mother of yours takes all the trouble

00:33:58.748 --> 00:34:03.841
and you get your Self-Realization.

00:34:06.494 --> 00:34:10.783
It will hardly take fifteen minutes.

00:34:12.494 --> 00:34:16.805
But those who don't want to have it should leave the hall.

00:34:17.006 --> 00:34:20.711
Because they cannot get it also.

00:34:20.912 --> 00:34:24.982
On the contrary, they will disturb you.

00:34:25.282 --> 00:34:31.197
If you have faith in yourself, I'm sure it will work out.

00:34:31.398 --> 00:34:35.492
You have to respect yourself,

00:34:36.069 --> 00:34:42.092
Because you are a human being at epitome of evolution.

00:34:53.839 --> 00:34:56.460
Now as I told you

00:34:56.661 --> 00:35:02.380
that this Kundalini, your Mother, knows everything about you.

00:35:03.094 --> 00:35:07.656
Please do not judge yourself.

00:35:08.396 --> 00:35:12.951
She knows, She judges you.

00:35:13.427 --> 00:35:22.325
So first condition is that you should not feel guilty at all.

00:35:25.332 --> 00:35:30.035
Whatever has happen in the past has happen.

00:35:30.337 --> 00:35:38.938
Why carry the guilty on your left side, this center?

00:35:39.618 --> 00:35:46.438
As a result of this mythical behaviour, you get spondylitis,

00:35:46.639 --> 00:35:49.564
or you get angina,

00:35:49.765 --> 00:35:53.223
or you get lethargic organs.

00:35:53.489 --> 00:35:59.051
You might even get diseases like tuberculosis.

00:35:59.252 --> 00:36:04.042
So why to carry this myth of guilt?

00:36:06.326 --> 00:36:10.974
You have to really forgive yourself.

00:36:11.175 --> 00:36:15.698
And should be pleasantly placed towards yourself.

00:36:15.977 --> 00:36:19.894
Even in My lecture, if you think that I have said something

00:36:20.095 --> 00:36:24.337
that makes you feel guilty, forget it.

00:36:25.727 --> 00:36:30.347
The second condition is even simpler

00:36:30.548 --> 00:36:33.832
if you understand it.

00:36:34.033 --> 00:36:38.728
You have to forgive everyone

00:36:38.929 --> 00:36:42.694
even without thinking about them,

00:36:42.895 --> 00:36:47.522
because it is a headache to think about it.

00:36:47.723 --> 00:36:54.660
Now, logically whether you forgive or don't forgive, what do you do?

00:36:55.346 --> 00:36:58.396
You don't do anything.

00:36:58.597 --> 00:37:06.315
But when you don't forgive, then you play into wrong hands and torture yourself.

00:37:08.244 --> 00:37:13.345
All your life, you tortured yourself.

00:37:13.546 --> 00:37:18.096
But at this moment is important to get this center

00:37:18.297 --> 00:37:24.409
and the center in the optic chiasma opened out.

00:37:24.899 --> 00:37:31.094
If you feel guilty, this center won't open and the Kundalini won't pass through.

00:37:31.363 --> 00:37:38.854
But the worst is the center on the optic chiasma which is constricted like this.

00:37:39.293 --> 00:37:42.327
And it won't open unless and until

00:37:42.528 --> 00:37:47.528
you forgive everyone without thinking about them.

00:37:47.769 --> 00:37:53.787
As it is you are playing into wrong hands and by not forgiving

00:37:53.988 --> 00:38:00.332
you will miss the most important thing that is your enlightenment.

00:38:01.990 --> 00:38:10.872
Third condition is very simpler that I request you to get out your shoes

00:38:12.561 --> 00:38:15.951
I'm sorry I have to say that because in England, first time I said:

00:38:16.160 --> 00:38:21.485
"Please take out your shoes", half of them left the hall.

00:38:28.212 --> 00:38:33.352
This help us to be in contact with the Mother Earth,

00:38:34.154 --> 00:38:38.193
which help us a lot.

00:38:41.209 --> 00:38:48.201
Now, you don't say any prays, any mantras, nothing.

00:38:49.057 --> 00:38:53.283
Please don't try to concentrate.

00:38:53.688 --> 00:38:58.908
Kundalini Itself will take your attention upward.

00:38:59.469 --> 00:39:03.508
Alright.

00:39:09.985 --> 00:39:13.816
Those who are sitting on the ground are alright.

00:39:14.017 --> 00:39:17.090
But those who are sitting on the chair have to keep

00:39:17.291 --> 00:39:21.595
both their feet apart from each other.

00:39:22.933 --> 00:39:27.667
Please all of you do it, otherwise you can go.

00:39:33.985 --> 00:39:40.165
Because the left and right are two powers.

00:39:40.645 --> 00:39:46.559
The left one is the power of desire

00:39:47.533 --> 00:39:52.790
And the right one is the power of action.

00:39:54.080 --> 00:40:02.017
First we tell you how to nourish your center with your self-confidence.

00:40:02.218 --> 00:40:04.675
These exercises have to be done only for tonight,

00:40:04.876 --> 00:40:09.586
afterwards you don't have to do anything.

00:40:10.969 --> 00:40:13.672
Now, so please put your left hand towards Me

00:40:13.873 --> 00:40:18.694
like this on your lap very comfortably sitting.

00:40:18.895 --> 00:40:25.543
Why he is not doing himself there? What is the matter with you?

00:40:26.372 --> 00:40:31.067
If you don't want to do, you can go out.

00:40:34.034 --> 00:40:37.523
obstinate.

00:40:42.113 --> 00:40:48.960
Alright. Now please understand that

00:40:49.161 --> 00:40:52.547
you have to be comfortable in your chair,

00:40:52.748 --> 00:40:57.509
but not slouch, not put one foot on top of other,

00:40:57.710 --> 00:41:02.275
but comfortably sitting.

00:41:04.497 --> 00:41:08.693
You don't have to go to Himalayas and stand on your head.

00:41:08.981 --> 00:41:13.192
You don't have to give up anything.

00:41:13.738 --> 00:41:19.339
I have told you it is not outside, but inside something has to happen.

00:41:20.708 --> 00:41:24.109
So please put your left hand on your lap,

00:41:24.310 --> 00:41:32.435
which is symbolizing that you have a desire to have your Self-Realization.

00:41:33.478 --> 00:41:38.396
Now put your right hand on your heart.

00:41:39.075 --> 00:41:48.015
We use our right hand for nourishing our centers on the left hand side.

00:41:48.216 --> 00:41:52.212
In the heart resides the Spirit.

00:41:52.413 --> 00:41:54.413
Please put left hand towards Me, try to understand,

00:41:54.614 --> 00:42:00.092
left hand towards Me and right hand on your heart, please.

00:42:01.854 --> 00:42:09.400
Now, we put our hand on the heart, where resides the Spirit.

00:42:10.410 --> 00:42:14.788
Now we take our right hand to the upper portion of abdomen

00:42:14.989 --> 00:42:19.790
on the left hand side.

00:42:19.991 --> 00:42:27.140
I've told you that if you become the Spirit, you become your master.

00:42:27.341 --> 00:42:35.512
So this is the center of your mastery, which is created by prophets and seers.

00:42:36.355 --> 00:42:43.355
Now, we take our right hand to the lower portion of abdomen

00:42:43.556 --> 00:42:47.556
on the left hand side.

00:42:48.332 --> 00:42:56.605
This is the center, surprisingly, is of pure divine knowledge.

00:42:57.347 --> 00:43:03.503
Now we take it up again in the upper portion of your abdomen.

00:43:03.704 --> 00:43:08.770
Then we take it on our heart.

00:43:09.005 --> 00:43:11.453
Then in the corner of the neck and shoulder

00:43:11.654 --> 00:43:16.646
and turn our head to right.

00:43:17.575 --> 00:43:21.582
I've already told you about this center.

00:43:21.929 --> 00:43:24.132
And quite that is in today with you,

00:43:24.333 --> 00:43:29.061
please don't feel guilty at all.

00:43:29.262 --> 00:43:34.098
I tell you, you have done nothing wrong.

00:43:34.299 --> 00:43:37.011
After all you are human beings and only human beings

00:43:37.212 --> 00:43:41.533
can commit mistakes, you are not gods.

00:43:42.435 --> 00:43:49.036
In Sahaja Yoga, there's no confession and there's no guilty.

00:43:49.503 --> 00:43:54.277
Is only love, compassion and forgiveness.

00:43:55.002 --> 00:44:05.033
Now, raise your right hand on top of your forehead across and put down your head.

00:44:05.234 --> 00:44:13.859
Here you have to forgive everyone without thinking about them.

00:44:15.836 --> 00:44:20.199
Now without feeling guilty, without counting your mistakes,

00:44:20.400 --> 00:44:24.830
just for your satisfaction, you have to ask forgiveness

00:44:25.031 --> 00:44:29.321
from the All-Pervading Divine Power.

00:44:30.340 --> 00:44:34.312
So take back your right hand on the back side of your head.

00:44:34.513 --> 00:44:38.732
This is the center for asking forgiveness.

00:44:39.172 --> 00:44:44.438
Now the last center, you have to stretch your palm fully.

00:44:44.723 --> 00:44:50.195
And put the center of your palm on top of fontanel bone area,

00:44:50.396 --> 00:44:57.132
which is a soft bone (...) your scalp.

00:44:57.590 --> 00:45:01.663
Now please, put down your head.

00:45:01.864 --> 00:45:05.919
And move your scalp seven times slowly.

00:45:06.364 --> 00:45:10.539
That is all you have to do.

00:45:10.740 --> 00:45:14.771
Now you have to close your eyes.

00:45:16.571 --> 00:45:20.965
Before that, see that you put your both the feet apart from each other

00:45:21.165 --> 00:45:25.321
and your left hand on your lap.

00:45:34.980 --> 00:45:46.753
Now, please close your eyes and don't open them till I tell you.

00:45:50.832 --> 00:45:54.870
Take down your hands now.

00:45:57.410 --> 00:46:01.441
And now put your right hand on your heart.

00:46:08.252 --> 00:46:11.036
Close your eyes.

00:46:11.236 --> 00:46:16.244
Now, here your have to ask Me a very fundamental question

00:46:16.445 --> 00:46:20.290
about yourself.

00:46:29.423 --> 00:46:34.860
You can call Me Mother or you can call Me Shri Mataji.

00:46:37.844 --> 00:46:42.566
So please say three times, ask a question:

00:46:42.766 --> 00:46:46.876
"Mother, am I the Spirit?"

00:47:01.108 --> 00:47:05.947
I have told already to you that if you become the Spirit,

00:47:06.147 --> 00:47:11.108
you become your own master.

00:47:16.767 --> 00:47:21.161
So please take your right hand upper portion of you abdomen

00:47:21.361 --> 00:47:24.846
on the left hand side.

00:47:28.517 --> 00:47:33.849
And here, you have to ask another fundamental question

00:47:34.049 --> 00:47:38.048
about yourself three times.

00:47:43.577 --> 00:47:46.471
Please ask Me in your heart three times:

00:47:46.671 --> 00:47:51.690
"Mother, am I my own master?"

00:48:00.250 --> 00:48:03.484
Now,

00:48:06.852 --> 00:48:13.305
I have already told you that I respect your freedom.

00:48:16.565 --> 00:48:24.385
And I cannot force on you the Pure Divine Knowledge.

00:48:28.685 --> 00:48:32.290
You have to ask for it.

00:48:32.490 --> 00:48:38.818
So please put down your hand in the left hand side of your abdomen,

00:48:44.535 --> 00:48:48.117
in the lower region.

00:48:48.317 --> 00:48:55.629
Here you ask again six times because this center has got six petals.

00:49:00.687 --> 00:49:08.820
Here you have to ask: "Mother, please give me Pure Divine Knowledge."

00:49:19.801 --> 00:49:25.765
Now, as soon as you ask for Pure Divine Knowledge,

00:49:25.965 --> 00:49:30.707
your Kundalini starts moving upward.

00:49:37.266 --> 00:49:44.382
So we have to nourish upper centers with your self-confidence.

00:49:49.557 --> 00:49:52.958
Please now put your right hand the upper portion of your abdomen

00:49:53.159 --> 00:49:57.210
on the left hand side.

00:50:02.229 --> 00:50:10.261
Here you have to say ten times with your full self-confidence:

00:50:10.462 --> 00:50:14.876
"Mother, I am my own master."

00:50:32.174 --> 00:50:37.748
At very outset, I told you that you are not this body, this mind,

00:50:37.948 --> 00:50:43.654
this intellect, these emotions, your ego or your conditionings,

00:50:43.854 --> 00:50:48.292
but you are the pure Spirit.

00:50:58.878 --> 00:51:02.482
So now please raise your hand on your heart

00:51:02.682 --> 00:51:07.785
and say again with full self-confidence twelve times:

00:51:07.986 --> 00:51:12.487
"Mother, I am the pure Spirit."

00:51:23.142 --> 00:51:29.653
This All-Pervading Divine Power is the ocean of knowledge

00:51:29.853 --> 00:51:33.783
of bliss.

00:51:42.025 --> 00:51:47.244
Ocean of bliss.

00:51:48.439 --> 00:51:56.517
It is the ocean of compassion and love.

00:51:59.540 --> 00:52:06.009
But above all, It is the ocean of forgiveness.

00:52:08.579 --> 00:52:11.864
So whatever mistakes your might have committed

00:52:12.064 --> 00:52:19.392
can be easily dissolved in the power of this ocean of forgiveness.

00:52:26.703 --> 00:52:31.683
So please, forgive yourself.

00:52:31.883 --> 00:52:36.151
And put your right hand in the corner of your neck and shoulder

00:52:36.351 --> 00:52:40.336
and push your neck to your right.

00:52:47.989 --> 00:52:54.047
Here you have to say, again, with full self-confidence sixteen times:

00:52:54.247 --> 00:52:59.319
"Mother, I am not guilty at all."

00:53:14.922 --> 00:53:23.562
I have already told you that you have to forgive everyone.

00:53:27.288 --> 00:53:34.124
Logically, whether you forgive or you don't forgive, you don't do anything.

00:53:39.096 --> 00:53:45.252
But if you don't forgive, then you play into wrong hands.

00:53:48.946 --> 00:53:58.360
So it is very important to forgive everyone without thinking about them.

00:54:04.743 --> 00:54:09.236
Leave them to the Divine Power to deal.

00:54:12.556 --> 00:54:21.962
Then you all raise your hand on top of your forehead across and please put down your head.

00:54:27.049 --> 00:54:35.744
Here you have to say from your heart not how many times:

00:54:41.898 --> 00:54:47.812
"Mother, I forgive everyone in general."

00:54:51.511 --> 00:54:54.647
At this moment, if you don't forgive,

00:54:54.847 --> 00:54:58.897
then this center which is so constricted won't open

00:54:59.097 --> 00:55:03.307
and the Kundalini cannot pass through it.

00:55:12.796 --> 00:55:17.878
Now without feeling guilty, without pointing your mistakes,

00:55:18.078 --> 00:55:23.042
for your satisfaction, you have to ask forgiveness

00:55:23.242 --> 00:55:27.476
from the All-Pervading Divine Power.

00:55:35.976 --> 00:55:39.190
So please take your right hand back side of your head

00:55:39.390 --> 00:55:43.780
and push back your head as far as possible.

00:55:49.752 --> 00:55:55.758
Here you have to say, again, from your heart, not how many times:

00:55:55.958 --> 00:56:03.071
"Oh, Divine Power, please forgive me if I have done anything wrong

00:56:03.271 --> 00:56:07.308
knowingly or unknowingly.

00:56:24.627 --> 00:56:30.447
Now the last center, which is very important.

00:56:33.919 --> 00:56:39.022
You have to stretch your hand fully, the palm fully

00:56:39.223 --> 00:56:47.774
and put the center of your palm on top of your fontanel bone area,

00:56:47.974 --> 00:56:53.037
it was a soft bone in your childhood.

00:57:04.629 --> 00:57:08.769
Now please put down your head.

00:57:10.574 --> 00:57:15.363
Please stretch your fingers outward.

00:57:17.433 --> 00:57:24.499
Here again I cannot force enlightenment on you,

00:57:24.699 --> 00:57:28.965
you have to ask for it.

